title: Faith in God's Plan
description:
This week, Sadie welcomes Multi-Platinum Recording Artist, Luke Bryan onto the podcast. Listen in as they discuss grief, Luke's journey to Nashville, and the greatest piece of advice he has ever received. Luke Bryan's latest album, Born Here, Live Here, Die Here released August 7th. You can learn more about Luke Bryan at www.lukebryan.com
